download and install go from url:https://golang.org/dl/
install eclipse from web（https://www.eclipse.org/downloads/）
install new software in eclipse from url:http://goclipse.github.io/releases/ (help:https://github.com/GoClipse/goclipse/blob/latest/documentation/Installation.md#installation)
download gocode from git:https://github.com/nsf/gocode and copy file to gopath and excute command : go build gocode. then config gocode in eclipse
download godef from git:https://github.com/rogpeppe/godef and copy file to gopath and excute command : go build godef. then config godef in eclipse
download goru from git:https://github.com/golang/tools and copy file to gopath/src/golang.org/x and excute command : go build tools/cmd/guru. then config goru in eclipse
install git from https://gitforwindows.org/
install mingw from https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win64/Personal%20Builds/rubenvb/gcc-4.8-release/